// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2496 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 9b62893b-15c0-5e2c-b4d9-adb97a91b4bd

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *chainguard:* OR ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14* OR ImageFileName = *wolfi:*)
